1
00:00:14,543 --> 00:00:19,981
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,816 --> 00:00:28,723
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,790 --> 00:00:34,160
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,229 --> 00:00:38,290
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,535 --> 00:00:44,438
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,173 --> 00:00:52,079
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,482 --> 00:00:56,974
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,052 --> 00:01:03,958
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,092 --> 00:01:11,157
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,233 --> 00:01:17,900
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,307 --> 00:01:27,875
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:49,415 --> 00:01:55,911
Sasuke!

13
00:01:59,592 --> 00:02:01,184
Are you going to
run away from me?!

14
00:02:21,314 --> 00:02:25,216
Yo... loser.

15
00:02:25,885 --> 00:02:30,618
<i>A Cry on Deaf Ears</i>

16
00:02:43,469 --> 00:02:45,061
It's you this time, huh?

17
00:02:49,709 --> 00:02:55,944
<i>I couldn't do it.</i>
<i>I was not able to stop Sasuke...</i>

18
00:02:57,317 --> 00:03:00,980
<i>I think...</i>
<i>the one who can stop Sasuke...</i>

19
00:03:01,788 --> 00:03:03,517
<i>the one who can save Sasuke is...</i>

20
00:03:04,958 --> 00:03:07,825
<i>Naruto...you are the only one.</i>

21
00:03:08,861 --> 00:03:14,356
<i>Naruto...this is my...</i>
<i>once in a lifetime...favor to ask...</i>

22
00:03:15,802 --> 00:03:19,704
<i>Please... Please bring Sasuke back!</i>

23
00:03:24,410 --> 00:03:26,310
I also told this to Sakura, but...

24
00:03:28,381 --> 00:03:30,542
Don't mind me anymore.

25
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:39,151
What's with that face?

26
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,167
<i>Iruka Sensei, why on the earth</i>
<i>does an outstanding person like me</i>

27
00:03:51,237 --> 00:03:53,569
<i>have to be on the same team with him?</i>

28
00:03:55,375 --> 00:03:58,538
<i>Sasuke graduated with</i>
<i>the highest grade out of all students...</i>

29
00:03:59,278 --> 00:04:01,212
<i>Naruto, you are at the bottom!</i>

30
00:04:01,914 --> 00:04:04,439
<i>When you even out</i>
<i>the team's strength,</i>

31
00:04:04,517 --> 00:04:06,041
<i>then it naturally becomes like this.</i>

32
00:04:07,053 --> 00:04:10,250
<i>Try your best not to slow me down,</i>
<i>you dunce.</i>

33
00:04:10,523 --> 00:04:16,860
<i>I am fine without eating!</i>
<i>I am absolutely fine.</i>

34
00:04:18,965 --> 00:04:20,091
<i>I'm...fine...</i>

35
00:04:22,068 --> 00:04:23,057
<i>Here.</i>

36
00:04:32,045 --> 00:04:37,881
<i>You asked Sakura for a hint the other day,</i>
<i>what did she tell you?</i>

37
00:04:41,821 --> 00:04:42,845
<i>Shall we go?</i>

38
00:04:43,423 --> 00:04:44,412
<i>Yup.</i>

39
00:04:50,096 --> 00:04:52,929
<i>Wh-What's with that face...?</i>

40
00:04:55,935 --> 00:04:58,699
<i>You loser...</i>

41
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:01,872
<i>Why...?</i>

42
00:05:03,376 --> 00:05:07,938
<i>You... I hated you, you know.</i>

43
00:05:11,884 --> 00:05:14,284
<i>It's none of your business!</i>

44
00:05:18,691 --> 00:05:25,324
<i>Who knows,</i>
<i>my body moved on its own.</i>

45
00:05:29,902 --> 00:05:33,668
<i>You rescue Sakura, no matter what!</i>

46
00:05:34,474 --> 00:05:37,068
<i>Sasuke... You...</i>

47
00:05:37,910 --> 00:05:42,370
<i>I could still distract him for a little while...</i>

48
00:05:43,649 --> 00:05:46,209
<i>I lost everything once.</i>

49
00:05:47,153 --> 00:05:54,184
<i>I don't want to see my precious comrades</i>
<i>die in front of me anymore.</i>

50
00:05:57,797 --> 00:05:58,764
Why...?

51
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:04,397
Why is it... Sasuke?

52
00:06:07,206 --> 00:06:10,141
Why did you become like this?!

53
00:06:10,209 --> 00:06:14,942
You!

54
00:06:20,953 --> 00:06:24,548
Whatever happens to me,
what does that have to do with you?

55
00:06:26,392 --> 00:06:28,292
I have my own way.

56
00:06:29,028 --> 00:06:30,859
No matter who it is,

57
00:06:30,930 --> 00:06:32,830
nobody has the right
to tell me what to do.

58
00:06:34,901 --> 00:06:36,334
I will tell you the truth.

59
00:06:39,238 --> 00:06:42,730
I'm done fooling around with
you guys of the Leaf.

60
00:06:44,477 --> 00:06:45,171
Go home.

61
00:06:59,125 --> 00:07:02,219
<i>I'll take care of him!</i>

62
00:07:02,628 --> 00:07:03,595
Choji...

63
00:07:03,663 --> 00:07:05,096
<i>Go everyone!</i>

64
00:07:07,867 --> 00:07:11,860
<i>Go, quickly! I'll catch up with you.</i>

65
00:07:12,872 --> 00:07:13,930
Neji...

66
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:15,136
<i>Okay!</i>

67
00:07:17,877 --> 00:07:18,969
<i>Hold on!</i>

68
00:07:25,518 --> 00:07:26,416
Kiba...

69
00:07:26,886 --> 00:07:29,081
<i>Kiba! Akamaru!</i>

70
00:07:31,657 --> 00:07:32,783
<i>Now! Naruto!</i>

71
00:07:34,827 --> 00:07:35,759
Shikamaru...

72
00:07:36,896 --> 00:07:37,920
<i>The strategy...a success!</i>

73
00:07:38,965 --> 00:07:41,399
<i>What are you doing?</i>
<i>Please go quickly!</i>

74
00:07:41,934 --> 00:07:46,928
<i>You also promised Sakura</i>
<i>with a Nice Guy pose, Naruto.</i>

75
00:07:47,607 --> 00:07:48,574
Bushy Brow...

76
00:07:48,975 --> 00:07:51,842
<i>I'll defeat this person.</i>

77
00:07:54,013 --> 00:07:54,945
<i>It's a promise.</i>

78
00:07:57,483 --> 00:07:58,609
Everyone...

79
00:08:00,786 --> 00:08:06,122
Everyone risked their lives
to come after you, you know!

80
00:08:08,527 --> 00:08:10,085
Good job for them.

81
00:08:24,176 --> 00:08:27,407
<i>Lastly, I will tell you</i>
<i>the most important thing.</i>

82
00:08:28,414 --> 00:08:34,375
<i>Sasuke is neither a close friend</i>
<i>of mine nor is he someone I like.</i>

83
00:08:35,254 --> 00:08:38,849
<i>But Sasuke is a Shinobi of</i>
<i>the Village Hidden in the Leaves...</i>

84
00:08:39,258 --> 00:08:40,520
<i>A comrade.</i>

85
00:08:40,893 --> 00:08:42,793
<i>That's why we will rescue him</i>
<i>by risking our lives.</i>

86
00:08:43,763 --> 00:08:45,287
<i>This is the Leaf way.</i>

87
00:09:04,984 --> 00:09:09,421
How do you take
your comrades of the Leaf?!

88
00:09:39,785 --> 00:09:41,184
Comrades, you said...

89
00:09:43,756 --> 00:09:48,159
Did I become stronger staying
with those so-called comrades?

90
00:09:50,129 --> 00:09:52,495
I am going to where Orochimaru is.

91
00:09:55,334 --> 00:09:58,269
Orochimaru is the person who killed
the Third Hokage

92
00:09:58,337 --> 00:10:00,828
and tried to crush The Leaf Village!

93
00:10:01,207 --> 00:10:04,836
Do you think he will
give you the power freely?

94
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:10,608
He just wants your body
as a vessel!

95
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:14,847
You might not be able to come back.
You might get killed.

96
00:10:15,221 --> 00:10:19,180
You think I'd easily let you
go to such a place?!

97
00:10:35,307 --> 00:10:37,332
That doesn't matter to me...

98
00:10:40,246 --> 00:10:43,374
If my goal is accomplished,
then that's all that matters.

99
00:10:45,251 --> 00:10:47,412
If you intend to get in that way...

100
00:10:48,687 --> 00:10:50,052
Then it can't be helped...

101
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:58,360
You're not gonna be able to!
I'll take you back even by force!

102
00:11:05,805 --> 00:11:07,466
Why are you laughing?!

103
00:11:08,607 --> 00:11:11,098
You were laughing at that time too.

104
00:11:12,878 --> 00:11:13,970
That time...?

105
00:11:14,513 --> 00:11:15,912
<i>What's funny?</i>

106
00:11:16,048 --> 00:11:19,279
<i>It's not funny. I am happy.</i>

107
00:11:20,052 --> 00:11:23,852
<i>Thinking about...</i>
<i>how I can finally defeat you here.</i>

108
00:11:26,225 --> 00:11:29,854
That time you wanted to fight me, right?

109
00:11:30,529 --> 00:11:32,292
You were thrilled weren't you?

110
00:11:32,565 --> 00:11:33,827
At first!

111
00:11:34,533 --> 00:11:37,127
But, you were different.

112
00:11:38,938 --> 00:11:40,064
That was...

113
00:11:40,873 --> 00:11:42,067
<i>Hurry up and come.</i>

114
00:11:42,141 --> 00:11:45,338
<i>But first, put on your Headband.</i>
<i>I'll wait.</i>

115
00:11:45,578 --> 00:11:47,637
<i>I don't need such a thing...</i>

116
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:49,575
<i>Just put it on!</i>

117
00:11:51,717 --> 00:11:56,745
<i>You won't be able to</i>
<i>put one scratch on my face.</i>

118
00:11:57,323 --> 00:11:58,255
<i>That's not it!</i>

119
00:11:58,691 --> 00:12:03,060
<i>I'm saying that this is a sign</i>
<i>that we fight as equal Leaf Shinobi.</i>

120
00:12:03,896 --> 00:12:06,160
<i>That is what I call a stuck up!</i>

121
00:12:06,499 --> 00:12:08,729
<i>You think you and I are equal?</i>

122
00:12:08,901 --> 00:12:10,596
<i>Yeah, I think so.</i>

123
00:12:10,836 --> 00:12:14,397
<i>I've never thought I was inferior to you.</i>

124
00:12:14,874 --> 00:12:16,466
<i>You're so obnoxious!</i>

125
00:12:17,009 --> 00:12:18,977
<i>Stop!</i>

126
00:12:31,023 --> 00:12:32,047
That was...

127
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:38,521
That was not the kind of fight I wanted.

128
00:12:40,699 --> 00:12:43,759
Even now... this is not...

129
00:12:45,571 --> 00:12:47,835
I don't care about
your circumstances.

130
00:13:51,768 --> 00:13:54,566
<i>What...is this power?</i>

131
00:13:57,974 --> 00:13:59,908
<i>Power is flowing out...</i>

132
00:14:18,294 --> 00:14:20,694
<i>So this is the power that</i>
<i>the guy was talking about.</i>

133
00:14:21,164 --> 00:14:24,793
<i>Furthermore, the power</i>
<i>is growing into my body.</i>

134
00:14:30,073 --> 00:14:35,136
<i>If it is like that now...</i>
<i>if I release this curse mark...</i>

135
00:14:38,848 --> 00:14:41,248
<i>I wonder how much power...</i>

136
00:14:52,495 --> 00:14:54,463
<i>Wh-What power...</i>

137
00:14:54,998 --> 00:14:57,899
<i>He's not the same as before...</i>

138
00:15:58,194 --> 00:16:00,685
Wake up already!

139
00:16:24,921 --> 00:16:26,912
I awakened long ago...

140
00:16:27,957 --> 00:16:32,189
From my idiotic self who dreams about
a lax peaceful future...

141
00:16:36,332 --> 00:16:38,493
hanging out with comrades.

142
00:16:40,436 --> 00:16:42,028
That's why I left the village!

143
00:16:43,006 --> 00:16:44,735
That's why I sought power!

144
00:16:45,642 --> 00:16:48,167
My dream is not in the future.

145
00:16:50,246 --> 00:16:52,043
My dream is in the past...

146
00:16:55,251 --> 00:16:56,684
That's the only place it exists.

147
00:17:50,273 --> 00:17:52,036
Wow, Brother!

148
00:17:52,108 --> 00:17:55,077
You hit the target right in the middle,
even the one behind the rock!

149
00:17:55,812 --> 00:17:58,246
All right, me too!

150
00:17:59,015 --> 00:18:00,949
Sasuke, let's go home.

151
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:07,153
Geez... You said that
you would teach me a new shuriken jutsu.

152
00:18:07,690 --> 00:18:12,252
There is an important mission tomorrow
and I need to prepare for that.

153
00:18:14,664 --> 00:18:16,188
Liar...

154
00:18:28,978 --> 00:18:32,209
Forgive me, Sasuke...
Another time.

155
00:18:37,754 --> 00:18:39,278
Brother, watch me!

156
00:18:40,924 --> 00:18:42,653
Hey! If you push yourself...

157
00:18:51,234 --> 00:18:54,101
Why is the one who twisted
his ankle laughing?

158
00:18:54,837 --> 00:18:58,068
Could it be that you are trying
to take the easy way?

159
00:18:58,441 --> 00:18:59,738
That's not true...

160
00:19:00,843 --> 00:19:02,037
I'm happy thinking about

161
00:19:02,111 --> 00:19:04,807
how I'm finally going to
the Academy starting tomorrow.

162
00:19:08,017 --> 00:19:10,247
<i>I'm going to do my best</i>
<i>when I enter the Academy.</i>

163
00:19:11,854 --> 00:19:15,551
<i>So even that father will approve of me.</i>

164
00:19:16,759 --> 00:19:19,284
<i>He will count on me</i>
<i>like he does on my brother...</i>

165
00:20:34,504 --> 00:20:39,100
Sasuke... You really are...

166
00:20:43,312 --> 00:20:44,643
I told you...

167
00:20:46,182 --> 00:20:49,583
I don't need a future
with you guys anymore.

168
00:20:54,824 --> 00:20:56,621
<i>Fire Style. Dragon Flame Jutsu.</i>

169
00:21:11,375 --> 00:21:13,775
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

170
00:21:13,844 --> 00:21:16,870
<i>And you smiled</i>

171
00:21:17,114 --> 00:21:19,412
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

172
00:21:19,483 --> 00:21:22,213
<i>In my own words</i>

173
00:21:22,286 --> 00:21:27,849
<i>Would you think it was</i>
<i>a bother if I approached you?</i>

174
00:21:28,192 --> 00:21:33,391
<i>Despite my doubts,</i>
<i>I worked up my courage</i>

175
00:21:33,664 --> 00:21:39,068
<i>My clumsy attempts with words</i>

176
00:21:39,269 --> 00:21:44,798
<i>You listened without turning away</i>

177
00:21:45,776 --> 00:21:50,975
<i>No wonder I get carried away by you</i>

178
00:21:51,381 --> 00:21:58,048
<i>But you don't feel anything for me, do you?</i>

179
00:21:58,555 --> 00:22:01,251
<i>I feel so sad</i>

180
00:22:01,325 --> 00:22:02,223
<i>But...</i>

181
00:22:02,292 --> 00:22:04,692
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

182
00:22:04,761 --> 00:22:07,730
<i>And you smiled</i>

183
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:10,458
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

184
00:22:10,534 --> 00:22:13,526
<i>In my own words</i>

185
00:22:13,704 --> 00:22:16,036
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

186
00:22:16,106 --> 00:22:19,234
<i>And you smiled</i>

187
00:22:19,309 --> 00:22:21,777
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

188
00:22:21,845 --> 00:22:24,746
<i>In my own words</i>

189
00:22:24,815 --> 00:22:29,377
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

190
00:22:37,794 --> 00:22:40,524
I feel power surging
through my body...

191
00:22:40,597 --> 00:22:42,565
It's as though I can't lose.

192
00:22:43,333 --> 00:22:48,168
It's power I'd never have gained
playing comrade with you guys from Leaf.

193
00:22:48,739 --> 00:22:53,369
But it's not enough.
It's way short of enough, Naruto!

194
00:22:54,511 --> 00:22:58,106
Strength... hatred... and desire!

195
00:22:58,582 --> 00:23:02,074
Next episode:
"Brothers: Distance Among the Uchiha"
